title: Maureen O'Hara, Irish-born star of The Quiet Man and more, dies aged 95
text: Maureen O'Hara, Irish-born star of The Quiet Man and more, dies aged 95 Saturday, 24 October 2015 (28 minutes ago) · Actor worked with John Wayne and John Ford in a number of films · Manager says Irish-born star died in her sleep at Idaho home The actor Maureen O’Hara has died, her manager said on Saturday. She was 95. Related: Philip French's screen legends Continue reading...
